social_posts.post_text:
Little @adidas test shoot I did with @johnnyb33__ about 2 hours total of shooting and I thought I’d share. What do y’all think? 

#adidas #commercial #commercialphotography #commercialphotographer #commercialphoto #commercialphotoshoot #dallasphotographer #dallasphotography
Went to NYC with the most amazing lady @m_lovesit to celebrate the birthday of @marcrebillet and @racstribling Mariah had never been to nyc before and we just had a magical time.

Marc at @erykahbadu’s birthday party in Dallas Texas 2-24-23 

So much fun and much more to come from this night.
The Queen of Dallas @erykahbadu birthday party @thefactoryde 2-24-23
@bigxthaplug @maxokream @bunb @raekwon @marcrebillet and many more showed out for @erykahbadu’s birthday last Friday. What an amazing time. Y’all gotta go next year!

Shot on the #pentax67 on #portra400 

Finally got around to getting my 120 developed recently. These shots are from the last 5ish months? I did digitally touch up a couple of these but nothing too significant. Absolutely love how these came out. Shoutout to @captive_photon for scanning these bad boys.
Saturday at Coachella with @marcrebillet and friends.
Coachella 23 with @marcrebillet and fam. Shot on the #pentax67 on a few different types of 120 @kodak film
Songs about fucking teaser y’all! A film by @gallagherwalks premieres June 10th at @tribeca film fest in NYC. I’ll see y’all there!

@tribeca weekend in NYC for @songs_about_fucking a film by @gallagherwalks 

Too many good photos to fit in 1 post

I cannot express how amazing it was to see everyone together to celebrate the premiere of Jame’s film. To be surrounded by such incredible people and the people I love so deeply was just wonderful. Can’t wait to see everyone again soon! Love y’all
